values: hello everyone i haven't updated in a while so my weekend went awsome i met a guy his name is justin he is such a sweetheart i absolutly love this kid friday night we sat talking from 11:00pm to 3:00am and then he wanted me to be his first so needless i say ya'llknow what happend i am so happy right now saturday was my X-Mas dance and i went with justin it was so sweet he opened the doors for me got me my drinks it was so romantic and the best part he's my little gothic angel he he he i looked so good in my dress i can't wait till i get my pictures.but back to my lifes story we came back home for once and i stayed at justin house he taught me how play hacke sack whooo i finally can play and then me and justin sat up all night again we just layed in his bed talking joking i can't believe i found my guy although flashy will always be my dream man he he he anyways i watched him fall asleep hes so cute i am oh so very happy today i dressed goth i fell at home with the baggy pants and shirts instead of dressing in very tight shirts well i gotta go so i will get on here more alright PEACE OUT love ya to all my friends Amanda

LOVE amanda
